description: Reserved Matters Application pursuant to conditions B1, B8 and Q1, Q4 of The Stratford City Outline Planning Permission (Ref: 10/90641/EXTODA) relating to details of layout, scale, design, appearance, access and landscaping. Comprising the construction of two buildings up to a maximum height of 30 storeys, providing 333 residential units, associated car parking and landscaped open space.
